'''宣言电台'''（{{lang-ar|البيان}}）是恐怖组织“[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]”的官方电台，总部位于[[伊拉克|伊拉克]][[摩苏尔|摩苏尔]]，在伊斯兰国控制的[[叙利亚|叙利亚]][[拉卡|拉卡]]、[[利比亚|利比亚]][[蘇特_(利比亞)|苏尔特]]等地也有播出。

==概况==
宣言电台2015年开播，使用[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]、[[库尔德语|库尔德语]]、[[英语|英语]]、[[法语|法语]]及[[俄语|俄语]]广播<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/islamic-state/11519977/Islamic-State-launches-English-language-radio-news-bulletins.html|title=Islamic State launches English-language radio news bulletins|publisher=[[每日电讯报|The Telegraph]]|agency=[[美联社|AP]]|accessdate=2016-05-04|date=2015-04-07|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711113143/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/islamic-state/11519977/Islamic-State-launches-English-language-radio-news-bulletins.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，内容涵盖新闻、谈话、[[古兰经|古兰经]]朗诵、[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]][[圣歌|圣歌]]及[[伊斯兰教法学|伊斯兰教法学]]等，而其新闻报道基本以伊斯兰国武装分子发动袭击的消息为主<ref name="pri">{{cite web|url=http://www.pri.org/stories/2015-04-22/thanks-listening-isis-radio-english|title=Thanks for listening to ISIS radio in English|publisher={{le|Public Radio International|Public Radio International}}|author=Leo Hornak|accessdate=2016-05-04|date=2015-04-22|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012084055/https://www.pri.org/stories/2015-04-22/thanks-listening-isis-radio-english|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2015年4月，该台开始播出英语新闻节目，而播音员的[[美式英语|美国口音]]也引发了关注，其“高度专业和精良的节目制作”以及播音员的语调也被一些西方传媒机构与[[BBC|BBC]]、[[NPR|NPR]]等媒体比较，甚至被指“与NPR可怕地相似”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2015/06/04/islamic-state-has-a-daily-english-language-radio-broadcast-that-sounds-eerily-like-it-could-be-on-npr/|title=Islamic State has an English-language radio broadcast that sounds eerily like NPR|publisher=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|author=Swati Sharma|accessdate=2016-05-04|date=2015-06-04|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825210044/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2015/06/04/islamic-state-has-a-daily-english-language-radio-broadcast-that-sounds-eerily-like-it-could-be-on-npr/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Lori Hinnant|agency=AP|title=The ISIS Radio Station Targeting Foreign Recruits Sounds Like NPR|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/the-isis-radio-station-targeting-european-recruits-sounds-like-npr-2015-6|accessdate=2016-05-04|work=[[商业内幕|Business Insider]]|date=2015-06-01|archive-date=2017-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171103232614/http://www.businessinsider.com/the-isis-radio-station-targeting-european-recruits-sounds-like-npr-2015-6|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pri"/>。

2017年，随着伊拉克军队逐步[[解放摩苏尔|收复摩苏尔]]，该台停播，据称已被伊斯兰国武装分子焚毁<ref>{{cite news|author=|agency=AFP|title=Iraqi troops stumble on Daesh media tentacle in Mosul|url=http://gulfnews.com/news/mena/iraq/iraqi-troops-stumble-on-daesh-media-tentacle-in-mosul-1.1987569|accessdate=2017-07-09|work=GULF NEWS|date=2017-03-03|archive-date=2017-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709132413/http://gulfnews.com/news/mena/iraq/iraqi-troops-stumble-on-daesh-media-tentacle-in-mosul-1.1987569|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

